  "description": "<p>Weekend getaways or epic through hikes, this versatile pack is designed to go where others falter. The body-hugging endurance waist belt has a ventilation channel and zippered mesh pockets for access to trail goodies. Ultra abrasion resistant Robic nylon handles the most rugged adventures while still being light enough to move quickly down the trail.</p><p>\uf0a7Spring steel wire frame is lightweight but rigid.</p><p>\uf0a7100D Robic recycled nylon ripstop and 330D Robic nylon in high-wear areas.</p><p>\uf0a7Breathable Endurance Yoke with running vest inspired mesh hydro pockets.</p><p>\uf0a7Slim wrap waistbelt with pockets for fast access to snacks or other trail essentials.</p><p>\uf0a7Two small interior dump pockets on the sides of the bag for extra storage.</p><p>\uf0a7Removable lid converts to a crossbody bag so you can bring a few items on side trips.</p><p>\uf0a7Drawstring access with full-length, double zipper for easy access to the main compartment.</p><p>\uf0a7Speed Zip\u2122 sleeping bag compartment with removable divider.</p><p>\uf0a7Front panel opens wide for easy access to your gear.</p><p>\uf0a7Dual adjustable attachments for tools or trekking poles.</p><p>\uf0a7Double daisy chains for lashing extra gear.</p><p>\uf0a7Side and bottom compression straps to cinch the load.</p>",
